com.adobe.dct.service

Interface DataDictionaryConfigurationService

  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface DataDictionaryConfigurationService
    DataDictionary Configuration Service exposes the DataDictionary configuration in the Felix web console's configuration tab. The last updated (current) value of the configurations can be retrieved/updated using the getter/setter methods of this services.
